---
layout: home.njk
title: ホーム
description: おうちヨガ・ウェルネスで毎日を整える。40〜50代女性のためのリアルな体験ブログ。
---

<style>
  /* ===== タブ ===== */
  .tab-wrap {
    display: flex;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .tab-btn {
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    border: none;
    background: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--grey-olive);
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -1px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--mauve); border-bottom-color: var(--mauve); }

  /* ===== 記事リスト ===== */
  .post-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .post-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 1.4rem;
    padding: 1.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .post-item:first-child { padding-top: 0; }

  .post-thumb-wrap { position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--radius); }
  .post-thumb {
    width: 100%; height: 136px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .post-item:hover .post-thumb { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .post-cat-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.5rem; left: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--mauve);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.12rem 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .post-body-inner { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.45rem; }
  .post-date { font-size: 0.73rem; color: var(--grey-olive); }
  .post-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--mauve);
  }
  .post-title a { color: var(--mauve); }
  .post-title a:hover { color: var(--dim-grey); }
  .post-excerpt {
    font-size: 0.81rem;
    color: var(--dim-grey);
    line-height: 1.7;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .post-more {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: var(--grey-olive);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .post-more::after { content: " →"; }
  .post-more:hover { color: var(--mauve); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .post-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<!-- タブ -->
<div class="tab-wrap">
  <button class="tab-btn active">新着記事</button>
  <button class="tab-btn">人気記事</button>
</div>

<!-- 記事リスト -->
<div class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
  <article class="post-item">
    <div class="post-thumb-wrap">
      <img class="post-thumb"
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&h=272&q=80"
        alt="{{ post.data.title }}">
      <span class="post-cat-badge">ヨガ体験談</span>
    </div>
    <div class="post-body-inner">
      <div class="post-date">{{ post.date | dateJP }}</div>
      <h2 class="post-title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
      {% if post.data.description %}
      <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-more">続きを読む</a>
    </div>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
